                                    <p>Yes. We give every patient the opportunity to have our full range of core enhanced preventive screenings, as well as age- and gender-appropriate evaluations for heart health, cancer, and other risks. But each visit is personalized for the patient, and you can opt not to certain components if you'd prefer.</p>
